    reseteo: `When {nombre} makes a mistake, their system may enter "technical analysis mode." Suggested accompaniment: Use logic. Do not ask them to forget it. Say: "The analysis was good, but the execution shifted because of X detail. Next time, adjust for that." By giving them a technical piece of data to adjust, their mind tends to "close" the mistake and return to the present with a clear improvement mission.`,
    ecos: `At home: They tend to prefer knowing the "why" behind agreements. They likely value you being consistent and following through on plans. They enjoy having their space and their materials organized in their own way. At school: They tend to have a very thorough academic profile, enjoying subjects with clear processes (mathematics, grammar, music). They tend to need to know exactly what is expected in an exam so they do not feel anxious.`,
