    ecos: `At home: They tend to need to understand the "why" of things. They likely do not accept "because I said so." They tend to value strategy games, puzzles, or any activity that requires planning greatly. At school: They may seem to be in their own world, but when asked, they have the deepest answer. They tend to love science, chess, or reading, where they can immerse themselves in logical systems.`,
